cs.CL, cs.CY, cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.DB

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language generation from data, which falls under the scope of computational linguistics. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of technology in healthcare, which has societal implications. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is another possible category as the paper discusses how technology can enhance patient experience of care. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of AI technology (data-to-text) in healthcare. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the influx of data from various sources in healthcare organizations.
